## How to attribute

If you reproduce, adapt, or build on this specification (for example, an
independent KAF implementation, a fork, or excerpts in a paper or post),
you must give appropriate credit. The recommended attribution is:

    Based on the Kindred Artifact Format (KAF) specification by
    Vlad Bordei, https://kindredformat.org — licensed under CC-BY-4.0.

Provide a link to the license, and indicate if changes were made.
